SELECT rp.property_name, r.rating_value, rr.review_text FROM rental_properties rp JOIN ratings r ON rp.property_id = r.property_id JOIN reviews rr ON r.tenant_id = rr.tenant_id WHERE r.rating_value > 4;

SELECT rp.property_name, COUNT(distinct r.tenant_id) as num_tenants, AR.average_rating FROM rental_properties rp LEFT JOIN ratings r ON rp.property_id = r.property_id LEFT JOIN average_ratings AR ON rp.property_id = AR.property_id GROUP BY rp.property_name, AR.average_rating HAVING num_tenants > 3;

SELECT rp.property_name, r.rating_value, rr.review_text FROM rental_properties rp JOIN ratings r ON rp.property_id = r.property_id JOIN reviews rr ON r.tenant_id = rr.tenant_id WHERE r.rating_value BETWEEN 3 AND 5 ORDER BY rp.property_name ASC, r.rating_value DESC;
